Class ViewPage2

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
View
ViewPage2
public class ViewPage2
extends View
This class is a subclass of view that will draw out the greenery tour page. It also presents the plant information page when a plant is selected and includes a slider to show back and forth between times
Author:
Lisa Pathania & Tara Fishman
